<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>{% block title %}Autorización de salida{% endblock %}</title>

    <link href="{{ asset('assets/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{ asset('assets/stylesheets/css/modern-business.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{ asset('assets/stylesheets/css/dashboard.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{ asset('assets/stylesheets/css/chart.min.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('logo.png') }}"/>
</head>

<body class="sb-nav-fixed">
    <div class="card" style="width: 70%; text-align: center; margin: auto">
        <div class="card-header text-white" style="background-color: #649154">
            AUTORIZACIÓN DE SALIDA
        </div>
        <div class="card-body" style="text-align: left">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body" style="text-align: left">
                    Estimados Padres y/o Tutores: <br>
                    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; El dia {{ when | date('d/m/Y') }} los/as
                    alumnos/as realizarán una visita a {{ where }} ubicado/a
                    en {{ address }}. La actividad se realizará dentro del horario
                    de clases. Para realizar dicha actividad es necesario que se
                    envíe al colegio la autorizacion firmada.<br>
                    <br>

                    <div style="float: right">Atentamente <i><strong>Semillitas de amor.</strong></i></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body" style="text-align: left">
                    Yo .......................................................... autorizo a ..........................................................
                    alumno/a del Centro de Cuidados Infantiles <strong>Semillitas de amor</strong> a realizar una visita a {{ where }} ubicado/a en {{ address }} el dia {{ when | date('d/m/Y') }}, dentro del
                    horario de clases ({{ startHour | date('H:i') }}- {{ endHour | date('H:i') }}).

                    <br><br><br><br>

                    <div align="center">
                        _________________________&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;_________________________ <br>
                        &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Firma &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Aclaración
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <button class="custom-button" id="btn-print">
            <i class="fa fa-print"></i> Imprimir
        </button>
    </div>
</body>

{% block javascripts %}
    <script src="{{ asset('assets/vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('assets/js/dashboard.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('assets/js/font-awesome.min.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('assets/js/chart.js') }}"></script>

    <script>
        $("#btn-print").on("click", function (ev) {

            $("#btn-print").css('display', 'none');
            print();
        })

        window.onafterprint = function(){
            $("#btn-print").css('display', 'inline-block');
        }
    </script>
{% endblock %}
